## Limitations

This report is based on information available up to October 2023 and may not reflect the most current developments in the chip shortage crisis. Additionally, the reliance on online sources means that some insights may be subject to bias or lack comprehensive coverage. The dynamic nature of global supply chains and geopolitical factors also means that the situation can change rapidly, potentially altering the conclusions drawn in this report.